Encounter Builder
Copyright 2014, Nicolas Maquet, Christophe Muylaert

INSTALLING DEPENDENCIES

    $ npm install

EXECUTING

    $ nodemon server/server.js

RUNNING CLIENT UNIT TESTS

    WebStorm > right-click on "karma-unit.conf.js" > Run
        or
    WebStorm > right-click on "karma-unit.conf.js" > Run with Coverage

RUNNING SERVER UNIT TESTS

    Create a new run configuration of type "Mocha" using test/server-unit as test directory.

RUNNING E2E TESTS

    WebStorm > right-click on "karma-e2e.conf.js" > Run
        or
    WebStorm > right-click on "karma-e2e.conf.js" > Run with Coverage (doesn't work yet)

USEFUL DOCS

    http://expressjs.com/api.html
    http://pivotal.github.io/jasmine/
    http://visionmedia.github.io/mocha/
    http://chaijs.com/
    http://karma-runner.github.io/
